  <p>CADU´s vision is to <b>develop of welfare</b>; therefore, our sustainability model is based on this premise and aims at developing integral cities with sustainable housing.</p>
  <p>Nowadays we know that Mexico faces a housing deficit of almost 9 million homes, meaning that there are millions of people
    (and millions of families) lacking access to decent affordable housing and basic services such as electricity, water and/or sanitation.
    That is why we are determined to contribute to the resolution of this problem.</p>
